<section><title>Description</title>
<!--use <ref> on all component names (other than the one indexed from this file) in this section only-->
  <p>The <tag>curve</tag><idx><tag>curve</tag></idx> component renders the graph of a spline when nested inside a <ref><tag>graph</tag></ref> component.  It can be used similarly to the <ref><tag>function</tag></ref> component, or it can be used in combination with the <ref><tag>bezierControls</tag></ref> component.  See examples below.</p>
</section> 

  
